# Summary Recompression Default (0.65)

This workspace now supports automatic one-pass rolling-summary recompression.

- Trigger threshold: `DISCOCLAW_SUMMARY_MAX_TOKENS` (default `1500`).
- Target ratio: `DISCOCLAW_SUMMARY_TARGET_RATIO` (default `0.65`).
- Effective recompression target: `floor(max_tokens * target_ratio)`.

When a freshly generated rolling summary exceeds the threshold, it is recompressed once and token estimates are logged before/after recompression.
